strings: <voice_0x01001188><se_low>*: Congratulations my child, you have reached your inner haven.
<voice_0x01001189><se_low>*: They passed the test and proved to be successors. believe me please
<voice_0x0100118B><se_low>*: It is your duty to protect this priceless heritage along with your wonderful children and grandchildren. This line should not be terminated.
<voice_0x0100118C><se_low>*: As long as this world exists, the world will be peaceful.
<voice_0x0100118D><se_high>Install on PC: Could he be our ancestor?
<voice_0x0100118E><se_def>Economy: specifically. This crystal looks like it was captured by the force shown in the image.
<voice_0x0100118F><se_high>Install on PC: He said<:> Do not lose the rope, but is it impossible? After all, we were adopted.
<voice_0x01001190><se_high>Install on PC: The family line ended with the death of his father.
<voice_0x01001191><se_def>Economy: It has nothing to do with increasing the success of the casino together.
<voice_0x01001192><se_def>Economy: At least don't forget to take the tourists home! You can get paid as a bodyguard until I get back!
<Cap><leader> Throw the crystal ball to the ground
